data.description: Come take a look at this remodeled home on 3.01 acres. There is fencing in the front yard and a gated driveway! There are 3 bedrooms 2 bath with a bonus room that could be a 4th BR with new carpet being added, hardwood floors, new laminate in the primary bedroom. Outside you will find a barn, acres of privacy and location that cannot be beat. Conveniently located in-between Bremen and Carrollton for easy access to I-20 and all the shopping/restaurants Carrollton has to offer. Please note the carpet is being replaced in the basement and the window is being fixed.
